parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can cause the doors to become inoperable, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to safety risks, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door handles break or fail to operate
the doors cannot be opened from the outside
the doors cannot be opened from the inside
the windows may malfunction or become stuck
the doors may unlock and open by themselves.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping and hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. In extreme cases, it can also cause the vehicle to roll away, resulting in property damage or injury.
symptoms: rough shifting from one gear to another

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ability to shift the transmission into neutral without the keys can cause the vehicle to roll away, resulting in accidents, property damage, or injury.
symptoms: Transmission can be shifted into neutral without the keys

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty door locking mechanism can cause doors to lock unexpectedly, making it difficult or impossible for occupants to exit the vehicle, which can lead to safety risks, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: Multiple doors (3 out of 4) lock unexpectedly
doors will not open from the outside
doors will not open from the inside.
